A [[exchange|currency_exchange]] allowing trade between bitcoins and USD (U.S. Dollar).

HelloBitcoin is the first Bitcoin exchange to offer margin trading (borrowing USDs to buy bitcoins) and shorting (borrowing BTCs to use for selling).

##Deposits

* BTC
* [[Dwolla]]
* Bank wire (Domestic)
* Bank wire (International)
* Physical check

##Withdrawals

* [[Dwolla]]
* Physical check
* Bank transfer (ACH)
* Bank wire (Domestic)
* Bank transfer (Interantional wire)

##History
The exchange was first available for beta testing on July 11, 2011 (4.1) and then opened registration to all in August, 2011.

